(551, 2, 'admin', 'teams_intro', '         &lt;p&gt;This tab is used during and after the contest. Teams are displayed there as they start participating.           &lt;p&gt;You can select a group at the top of the &quot;group&quot; column to display the teams of this group. You can input the name of a student at the top of the &quot;students&quot; column, to check her participation time, her access code or her score.&lt;/p&gt;             &lt;p&gt;If you notice an error in the names of students, go to the &quot;Students&quot; tab to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;', 0),
(552, 2, 'admin', 'teams_delete_selected', 'Delete the selected team', 0),
(553, 2, 'admin', 'contestants_intro', '            &lt;p&gt;This tab is useful after the contest. It can be used to fix any mistakes in the names and genre of students. For this, we will indicate which student''s last names or first names are likely to be &quot;incorrect&quot;. &lt;/p&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                &lt;i&gt;To modify data in the grid below (last name, first name or genre of a student), select the row, then click on the cell you want to change. &lt;b&gt;Press enter when you''re done editing it&lt;/b&gt; to save your changes.&lt;/i&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;', 0),
(554, 2, 'admin', 'contestants_delete_selected', 'Delete the selected student', 0),
(555, 2, 'admin', 'certificates_intro', '            &lt;p&gt;             Here, you can generate and print participation certificates for each of the students &lt;b&gt;who took part in the contest&lt;/b&gt;.Here is an             &lt;a href=&quot;images/diplomeExemple.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ici&lt;/a&gt; example of certificate.             &lt;/p&gt;             &lt;p&gt;             This feature is not available for unofficial participants&quot;.             &lt;/p&gt;             &lt;p&gt;             Before asking for the generation of certificates, please check:             &lt;/p&gt;             &lt;ul&gt;             &lt;li&gt;that you provided your title (Mr./Mrs.) in the &quot;Coordinator&quot; tab,&lt;/li&gt;             &lt;li&gt;that you provided the correct school name in the &quot;School tab&quot;, as it should appear on the certificate,&lt;/li&gt;             &lt;li&gt;that the names of the students are all correct in the &quot;Students&quot; tab.&lt;/li&gt;             &lt;/ul&gt;             &lt;p&gt;             Once you have checked all this, you just have to ask for the generation of certificates, below. To reduce the number of files to download, all of the certificates will be downloadable as a single pdf file. You can also choose to get a pdf for each group.             &lt;/p&gt;             &lt;p&gt;             Don''t hesitate to contact us if you have questions.             &lt;/p&gt;', 0),
